reviewText:
The game itself has a very unqiue art style with still drawing animation and very well drawn and semi-animated comic book like epic fantasy characters, the intro is very well made and the story is ok, allthou the fact in lacks in alot of story. :P
This game is a excelent perception test and the opening of chests is like a IQ test game -allthou they are fairly easy at start later on become chalenging. I dont know who would apriciate a counter above his or hers  head while he or she is tryng to play somthing. The game is very good -especially the option to reproduce gems and gold by quests suprised me pleasantly -only to disapoint me even more when i hit the paywall of it. What i really dont like is it takes real money to be able to participate in the game and progress normaly in it that is a huge downfall for this game, there is the option to wait and all but that takes ages (to make you pay). A very well made game and i hope it will get a better gameplay concept then actual paying for another step or time in the game. But still there is alot of effort putten into it and the makers are obviously looking for a way to earn their invested money back and profit at the same time-which is normal.- But basing the whole gameplay on that is rather to say the least anyoing to players that are actually interested in this game, and undermines the real value or enjoyment of the artstile by monetasing it.  But the game is fun and interesting and very well made and chalenging. However i would say No thank you- to this.

;-}
